  <title>Equivalencias num&eacute;ricas &middot; Nivel Dif&iacute;cil &middot; Kinest&eacute;sico</title>

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
